Subject:Re: [Antenna-discussion] 1/2-wave vertical really needs a ground
	plane?
Hi Zilvinas
Well, there is no exact answer, but you can assume 5/8 lambda is the
same as 1/2 lambda, there is not much difference in the requirements
for the ground wires.
Alan G3NOQ



